data.eml:eml: Sipunculans of the Caribbean coast of Venezuela and Curaçao

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Dean, Harlan K., Hernández-Ávila, Iván, Cutler, Edward B. (2007): Sipunculans of the Caribbean coast of Venezuela and Curaçao. Zootaxa 1431: 45-54, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.175810
